org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.protocol
Class SnapshotDiffReport

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.protocol.SnapshotDiffReport

public class SnapshotDiffReport
extends Object

This class represents to end users the difference between two snapshots of the same directory, or the difference between a snapshot of the directory and its current state. Instead of capturing all the details of the diff, which is stored in INodeDirectorySnapshottable.SnapshotDiffInfo, this class only lists where the changes happened and their types.
